            <lg xml:id="TK66">
<l>kuḻaliṉi tiyāḻiṉi teṉpatam makkaṇ</l>
<l>maḻalaiccoṟ kēḷā tavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>"The pipe is sweet," "the lute is sweet"—say they who have not heard</l>
<l>their children's prattling words.</l>
            </lg>
